---
import ContentPageLayout from '../../layouts/ContentPageLayout.astro';

const blogSchema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Blog',
  name: 'Trees Puzzle Blog',
  url: 'https://treespuzzle.com/blog/',
  inLanguage: 'en',
};
---

<ContentPageLayout
  title="Trees Puzzle Blog | Nature Learning Guides and Outdoor Activity Ideas"
  heading="Trees Puzzle Blog"
  description="Browse tree puzzle ideas, printable nature activities, leaf identification games, and forest scavenger hunt guides."
  canonicalPath="/blog/"
  schemas={[blogSchema]}
>
  <p>This editorial hub collects the main teaching guides on Trees Puzzle. Start with the core activity pages, then expand into printables and FAQs.</p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-6">
    <a href="/tree-puzzle-ideas/" class="bg-ink-900/60 border border-ink-700/50 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-brand-500/50 transition-colors">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-ink-500 mb-2">Core guide</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl text-white font-semibold mb-2">10 tree puzzle ideas for kids</h2>
      <p class="text-ink-400 text-sm">Low-prep activity ideas that combine observation, movement, and matching.</p>
    </a>

    <a href="/leaf-identification-puzzles/" class="bg-ink-900/60 border border-ink-700/50 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-brand-500/50 transition-colors">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-ink-500 mb-2">Cluster</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl text-white font-semibold mb-2">Leaf identification puzzles</h2>
      <p class="text-ink-400 text-sm">Spot patterns in shape, edges, veins, and seasonal change.</p>
    </a>

    <a href="/forest-scavenger-hunt/" class="bg-ink-900/60 border border-ink-700/50 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-brand-500/50 transition-colors">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-ink-500 mb-2">Cluster</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl text-white font-semibold mb-2">Forest scavenger hunt clues</h2>
      <p class="text-ink-400 text-sm">Guide children toward noticing texture, canopy, seeds, and habitats.</p>
    </a>

    <a href="/printables/" class="bg-ink-900/60 border border-ink-700/50 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-brand-500/50 transition-colors">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-ink-500 mb-2">Resource</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl text-white font-semibold mb-2">Printable tree activity pack</h2>
      <p class="text-ink-400 text-sm">A launch-ready page for worksheets, clue cards, and matching grids.</p>
    </a>

    <a href="/faq/" class="bg-ink-900/60 border border-ink-700/50 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-brand-500/50 transition-colors md:col-span-2">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-ink-500 mb-2">FAQ</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl text-white font-semibold mb-2">Frequently asked questions</h2>
      <p class="text-ink-400 text-sm">Quick answers on age range, setup, safety, and printable use.</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</ContentPageLayout>
